Tool = script.Parent
local stillEquipped = false
function onEquippedLocal(mouse) stillEquipped = true if mouse == nil then print("Mouse not found") return end while stillEquipped do print("Setting Mouse to go") mouse.Icon = "rbxasset://textures\\GunCursor.png" while Tool.Enabled and stillEquipped do wait(0.01) end print("Setting Mouse to wait") mouse.Icon = "rbxasset://textures\\GunWaitCursor.png" while not Tool.Enabled and stillEquipped do wait(0.01) end end end

local Tool = script.Parent local Sword = Tool.Handle
local vCharacter local myTorso local myHumanoid local vPlayer
Tool.Enabled = true
local runService = game:service("RunService")
local damage = 17
local dashTime = 0 local lastKeyDown = 0
local debris = game:GetService("Debris") local runService = game:service("RunService")
local slashAnim local swordWalkAnim local shootAnim
function shootGun(key) key = key:lower() if key == "w" then t = runService.Stepped:wait() if (t - lastKeyDown < 0.2) then dashTime = t end lastKeyDown = t elseif key == "q" then local fireGun = Tool:FindFirstChild("FireGun") if fireGun and fireGun.Value == false then shootAnim = myHumanoid:LoadAnimation(Tool.ShootAnim) if shootAnim then shootAnim:Play() end wait(0.1) fireGun.Value = true end end end
function tagHumanoid(humanoid, player) if humanoid then local creatorTag = Instance.new("ObjectValue") creatorTag.Name = "creator" creatorTag.Value = player creatorTag.Parent = humanoid debris:AddItem(creatorTag, 1) end end
function blow(hit) if hit and hit.Parent then local humanoid humanoid = hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") if hit.Parent:IsA("Hat") and hit.Parent.Parent then humanoid = hit.Parent.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") end if humanoid and myHumanoid and humanoid ~= myHumanoid then tagHumanoid(humanoid, vPlayer) humanoid:TakeDamage(damage)
if hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("PoisonScript") == nil then local freezeScript = Tool.PoisonScript:Clone() freezeScript.Parent = hit.Parent freezeScript.Disabled = false end end end end
function onActivated() if Tool.Enabled == false then return end
if myTorso == nil or myHumanoid == nil then return end
Tool.Enabled = false
t = runService.Stepped:wait()
slashAnim = myHumanoid:LoadAnimation(Tool.Slash) if slashAnim then slashAnim:Play() end
wait(0.2)
local fireGun = Tool:FindFirstChild("FireGun") if fireGun and fireGun.Value == false then fireGun.Value = true end
wait(1.0)
Tool.Enabled = true
end
function onEquipped(mouse) vCharacter = Tool.Parent myTorso = vCharacter:FindFirstChild("Torso") myHumanoid = vCharacter:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") vPlayer = game.Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(vCharacter)
if myHumanoid then swordWalkAnim = myHumanoid:LoadAnimation(Tool.SwordWalkAnim) if swordWalkAnim then swordWalkAnim:Play() end end
if mouse then mouse.KeyDown:connect(shootGun) end end
function onUnequipped() if slashAnim then slashAnim:Stop() end if throwAnim then throwAnim:Stop() end if swordWalkAnim then swordWalkAnim:Stop() end if shootAnim then shootAnim:Stop() end end
Tool.Activated:connect(onActivated) Tool.Equipped:connect(onEquipped) Tool.Unequipped:connect(onUnequipped)
Sword.Touched:connect(blow)

local Tool = script.Parent local Sword = Tool.Handle
local vCharacter local myTorso local myHumanoid
Tool.Enabled = true
local pirateGun local pirateGunWeld local pirateGunMesh
local bullet = Instance.new("Part") bullet.FormFactor = 3 bullet.Shape = "Ball" bullet.Size = Vector3.new(0.5, 0.5, 0.5) bullet.CanCollide = true bullet.Transparency = 0.0
local bulletMesh = Instance.new("SpecialMesh") bulletMesh.MeshId = "http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=50876274" bulletMesh.TextureId = "" bulletMesh.VertexColor = Vector3.new(1, 1, 0) bulletMesh.Parent = bullet bulletMesh.Scale = Vector3.new(0.03, 0.03, 0.03)
local debris = game:GetService("Debris")
local shootSound
function tagHumanoid(humanoid, player) if humanoid then local creatorTag = Instance.new("ObjectValue") creatorTag.Name = "creator" creatorTag.Value = player creatorTag.Parent = humanoid debris:AddItem(creatorTag, 1) end end
function blow(bullet, hit) if hit == nil or hit.Parent == nil or vCharacter == nil then return end local humanoid = hit.Parent:findFirstChild("Humanoid") if hit.Parent:IsA("Hat") and hit.Parent.Parent then humanoid = hit.Parent.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") end if humanoid ~= nil and humanoid ~= myHumanoid and myHumanoid ~= nil then tagHumanoid(humanoid, vPlayer) humanoid:TakeDamage(21) end if bullet then bullet:Remove() end end
function shoot(direction)
vCharacter = Tool.Parent
spawnPos = myTorso.Position spawnPos = spawnPos + direction.unit * 5.0
local bulletC = bullet:Clone() bulletC.CFrame = CFrame.new(spawnPos, spawnPos + direction) bulletC.Parent = game.Workspace
local bodyForce = Instance.new("BodyForce") bodyForce.force = Vector3.new(0.0, bulletC:GetMass() * 196.1, 0.0) bodyForce.Parent = bulletC
bulletC.Velocity = direction.unit * 50.0
bulletC.Touched:connect(function(hit) blow(bulletC, hit) end)
debris:AddItem(bulletC, 2) end
function onEquipped() vCharacter = Tool.Parent myTorso = vCharacter:FindFirstChild("Torso") myHumanoid = vCharacter:FindFirstChild("Humanoid")
leftArm = vCharacter:FindFirstChild("Left Arm")
if vCharacter and vCharacter:FindFirstChild("PirateGun") == nil and leftArm then pirateGun = Instance.new("Part") pirateGun.FormFactor = 3 pirateGun.Size = Vector3.new(1.5, 1.5, 1.5) pirateGun.CanCollide = false pirateGun.Name = "PirateGun" pirateGun.Parent = vCharacter
pirateGunMesh = Instance.new("SpecialMesh") pirateGunMesh.MeshId = "http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=71525762" pirateGunMesh.TextureId = "http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=71525769" pirateGunMesh.Scale = Vector3.new(1.2, 1.2, 1.2) pirateGunMesh.Parent = pirateGun
pirateGunWeld = Instance.new("Weld") pirateGunWeld.Part0 = leftArm pirateGunWeld.Part1 = pirateGun pirateGunWeld.C1 = CFrame.new(0, -1.90000021, -0.399999976, 1, 0, 0, 0, -1, 8.74227766e-008, 0, -8.74227766e-008, -1) pirateGunWeld.Name = "PirateGunWeld" pirateGunWeld.Parent = leftArm end end
function onUnequipped() if pirateGun then pirateGun:Destroy() end if pirateGunWeld then pirateGunWeld:Destroy() end if shootSound then shootSound:Stop() end end
Tool.Equipped:connect(onEquipped) Tool.Unequipped:connect(onUnequipped)
while Tool:FindFirstChild("FireGun") == nil do wait() end
local fireGun = Tool.FireGun
fireGun.Changed:connect(function() if fireGun and fireGun.Value == true and myHumanoid and myTorso and pirateGun then local target = myHumanoid.TargetPoint local direction = (target - myTorso.Position).unit shootSound = Sword:FindFirstChild("ShootSound") if shootSound then shootSound:Play() end shoot(direction) wait(1.0) fireGun.Value = false end end)

local vCharacter = script.Parent local myHumanoid = vCharacter:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") local myTorso = vCharacter:FindFirstChild("Torso")
local duration = 3.5
local fire
if myHumanoid then if myTorso then fire = Instance.new("Fire") fire.Parent = myTorso fire.Color = Color3.new(0, 1, 0) fire.SecondaryColor = Color3.new(0, 1, 0) end while duration > 0 do duration = duration - wait(0.5) myHumanoid:TakeDamage(3.5) wait(0.5) end if fire then fire:Destroy() end end
wait(1.75) script:Remove()
